
                        Section 2 - Notes
                        USER Instruction

1.  Initial Dockerfile, build image and run.

    $ cat Dockerfile
    FROM ubuntu
    USER games:games
    CMD ["/bin/bash"]

    $ docker build -t user . 
    $ docker run -it user
    games@fc22c5b426ff:/$ id
    uid=5(games) gid=60(games) groups=60(games)

2.  Next Dockerfile, build image and run.

    $ cat Dockerfile
    FROM ubuntu
    USER 10:10
    CMD ["/bin/bash"]

    $ docker build -t user . 
    $ docker run -it user
    uucp@65cd383e08dc:/$ id
    uid=10(uucp) gid=10(uucp) groups=10(uucp)

